title: Breaking Down NFL Mock Draft 2.0 and Winners and Losers of the NFL Combine's Cancellation
description:
Kaelen Jones is joined by The Ringer’s Danny Kelly to discuss some of the top prospects in his latest mock draft (2:02). Then they are joined by The Ringer’s Rodger Sherman to pick out who the winners and losers are after the league announced there won't be an in-person combine this year (36:10). 

Host: Kaelen Jones
Guests: Danny Kelly and Rodger Sherman
